{"tid":1163635,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【FB開火】黃之鋒入獄曹永廉揶揄「快啲香」","createTime":"2019-05-20T14:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T15:30:19.000Z","uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20dc4657e852a62dd459033e2420981b9b2ac64f","tid":1163635,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"【FB開火】黃之鋒入獄曹永廉揶揄「快啲香」 網民鬧爆：去大灣區啦你！<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0520 13:00<br />\n<br />\n隨着科技發展，今時今日的都市人少不免都會有手提電話，而於各大社交平台交流，亦已經成為我們日常生活的一部份，不少人都會於網上發表意見，當中當然包括政見。不過近年香港政治矛盾慢慢加深，不少對政治有不同見解的人常常於網上開火，而今日的主角，則為54歲的大台藝人曹永廉。<br />\n<br />\n日前有網民於社交平台討論區貼出黃之鋒上訴案詳情（新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2WVdMpN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WVdMpN&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGVLtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=86bff7c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2WVdMpN</a> ），更揶揄需即時入獄2個月的黃之鋒，稱「除咗恭喜，都唔知講乜好，恭喜恭喜。」本來只是網上一個非常等閒的留言，卻引來曹永廉用FB私人賑號讚好，曹永廉更留言追擊黃之鋒：「希望佢快啲香」，結果惹來大批網民鬧爆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有網民起初都懷疑曹永廉的身份，不過有細心的網民發現，此賑戶確為曹永廉的私人FB，網民即群起反擊：「佢星途都好快香」，又有人不憤曹永廉「冇口德」，稱：「你香佢都未香，你以後拍嘅戲唔會再有人睇！」該名網民其後繼續狙擊：「曹永廉，你係公眾人物，你用真身講嘢預咗人哋畀評語你㗎啦！思想同鄰國一樣，喺香港冇人睇你㗎喇！去大灣區發展啦你！」而曹永廉後來亦有回覆表示：「無謂同廢物嘈。」"},{"pid":"3827ff1599550be522d7cb928d6ea121a24c62df","tid":1163635,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190520/59620615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59620615&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGVLtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=2d8ad4a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59620615&h=5349d256\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190520/59620615</a>"},{"pid":"3305ccb2d4bef422ed69740114649d792aeadbbd","tid":1163635,"uid":46042,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"曹永廉係香港撈 又要同香港人作對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33b68621a0a7be14e53605397997304ba1485a9","tid":1163635,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2817552/org/c31e4ecbf7630ea0186dd879ba796d94.png/WwQ4ZYccmmzUVbGLkNZf1vXRBzk4gZLgDneA5Q53gOU?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2817552%2Forg%2Fc31e4ecbf7630ea0186dd879ba796d94.png%2FWwQ4ZYccmmzUVbGLkNZf1vXRBzk4gZLgDneA5Q53gOU%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=fd53f88d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08ba5aeb93727acb62979c6d77e622053b12bab6","tid":1163635,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2817571/org/6fdc9328a2397936f25282d0619ff1dc.jpg/cjcGrbH8TwCG4RlPsBvwR-rjx4rElN3MRe7dDEXu3Qw?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2817571%2Forg%2F6fdc9328a2397936f25282d0619ff1dc.jpg%2FcjcGrbH8TwCG4RlPsBvwR-rjx4rElN3MRe7dDEXu3Qw%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=c4f7e329&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26a64ac416d9f458413c2bc380a652af802b1fd8","tid":1163635,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2818963/org/42c61e1e9bb6446bbbb65449771a34f0.jpg/SJ8v1-Eh1WVQgdFc2EZ2rTqAuyEj7lW1E6_GqxOvxqs?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2818963%2Forg%2F42c61e1e9bb6446bbbb65449771a34f0.jpg%2FSJ8v1-Eh1WVQgdFc2EZ2rTqAuyEj7lW1E6_GqxOvxqs%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=7dd10854&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f38661e92247bfd4baff3eb08f1e0338523f219","tid":1163635,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"「曹永廉」FB留言狙擊黃之鋒 用簡體字發表偉論真係本尊 ?<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒因2014年佔旺清場期間，阻撓執達主任在旺角清場而被控違反法庭禁制令，5月16日雖上訴得直，把入獄3個月減至入獄2個月，但須即時入獄服畢餘下刑期。相關新聞（連結按此）播出後，亦有不同政見市民於社交網站轉發或留言表達己見，有人支持黃之鋒，當然亦有人反對，日前更有網民於Facebook討論區中留言揶揄：「除咗恭喜，都唔知講乜好，恭喜恭喜。」"},{"pid":"238b1403c2385112de5fc923761b87b0960cb5e2","tid":1163635,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒5月16日到庭時被大批傳媒包圍。（李澤彤攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2817424/org/30912b1549e41de799aaea31067e1012.jpg/h1VDAkvVGR9D56O5mIJMaac6Z8IkTEelIHOdhwpznYc?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2817424%2Forg%2F30912b1549e41de799aaea31067e1012.jpg%2Fh1VDAkvVGR9D56O5mIJMaac6Z8IkTEelIHOdhwpznYc%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=7686f125&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"620751054ad5513125ba4bed7f525af0a1758279","tid":1163635,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:35:08.000Z","msg":"其實這些網上言論只屬日常千萬個留言之一，普通的不得了，但卻引來疑似是TVB藝人曹永廉的注意。近日有網民發現，一個Facebook帳號「曹永廉」在該篇文章底下讚好，以及留言：「被佔中影響嘅市民，到現在可能家庭破裂，一無所有，呢個判決公平嗎？法治已死！」更在網民留言中追擊黃之鋒：「希望佢快啲香」。結果，留言一出，「曹永廉」反倒成為網民攻擊的對象。有網民更留言表示，他身因為公眾人物就應該要有操守，也有人留言：「你香佢都未香，你以後拍戲唔會有人睇！」、「詛咒人真係好唔啱，他真係會有報應！」<br />\n<br />\n不過，經記者查找所得，廿多日前該Facebook帳號「曹永廉」亦在另一個討論中，以簡體字留言批評政府以及表達對香港法治的不滿，所以，到底這個「曹永廉」是否真的是曹永廉本人，抑或只是被人冒充呢？就真的要待他本人解答了。而《香港01》亦曾聯絡曹永廉，但暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2817640/org/539fecd7fcc29846e5c437f3a5f98193.jpg/Kz-4WSkKtt27TtFyDIyoBtGZp4EhhRoVwjYeZsI2HmY?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2817640%2Forg%2F539fecd7fcc29846e5c437f3a5f98193.jpg%2FKz-4WSkKtt27TtFyDIyoBtGZp4EhhRoVwjYeZsI2HmY%3Fv%3Dw800&h=14a07b6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f17057e9638d99b679f9965b7eea9af4730804b","tid":1163635,"uid":2002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"想問同期有無人好似佢咁霉"},{"pid":"